Q1 . Simple Contact Form: Create an HTML form for a contact page. Include fields for:
Name (text input)
Email (email input)
Subject (text input)
Message (textarea)
Submit button
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Simple Contact Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Contact Us</h1>

  <!-- HTML Form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Name input -->
    <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

    <!-- Email input -->
    <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>

    <!-- Subject input -->
    <label for="subject">Subject:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject"><br><br>

    <!-- Message textarea -->
    <label for="message">Message:</label><br>
    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" cols="30"></textarea><br><br>

    <!-- Submit button -->
    <input type="submit" value="Send Message">
  </form>
</body>
</html>


Q2. User Registration Form: Design a registration form with fields for:
Username (text input)
Password (password input)
Confirm Password (password input)
Gender (radio buttons)
Country (dropdown select with multiple options)
Accept Terms & Conditions (checkbox)
Register button

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>User Registration Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>User Registration</h1>

  <!-- Registration form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Username -->
    <label for="username">Username:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required><br><br>

    <!-- Password -->
    <label for="password">Password:</label><br>
    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required><br><br>

    <!-- Confirm Password -->
    <label for="confirm">Confirm Password:</label><br>
    <input type="password" id="confirm" name="confirm" required><br><br>

    <!-- Gender (radio buttons) -->
    <label>Gender:</label><br>
    <input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="Male">
    <label for="male">Male</label>
    <input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="Female">
    <label for="female">Female</label><br><br>

    <!-- Country (dropdown select) -->
    <label for="country">Country:</label><br>
    <select id="country" name="country">
      <option value="">--Select Country--</option>
      <option value="india">India</option>
      <option value="usa">USA</option>
      <option value="uk">UK</option>
      <option value="australia">Australia</option>
    </select><br><br>

    <!-- Accept Terms & Conditions (checkbox) -->
    <input type="checkbox" id="terms" name="terms" required>
    <label for="terms">I accept the Terms & Conditions</label><br><br>

    <!-- Register button -->
    <input type="submit" value="Register">
  </form>
</body>
</html>



Q3. Appointment Booking Form: Build a form for booking an appointment. (Utilize HTML5)
Date (date input)
Time (time input)
Number of attendees (number input with min/max values)
Preferred color (color input)
Submit button
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Appointment Booking Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Book an Appointment</h1>

  <!-- Appointment form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Date input -->
    <label for="date">Select Date:</label><br>
    <input type="date" id="date" name="date" required><br><br>

    <!-- Time input -->
    <label for="time">Select Time:</label><br>
    <input type="time" id="time" name="time" required><br><br>

    <!-- Number of attendees -->
    <label for="attendees">Number of Attendees:</label><br>
    <input type="number" id="attendees" name="attendees" min="1" max="10" required><br><br>

    <!-- Preferred color -->
    <label for="color">Preferred Color:</label><br>
    <input type="color" id="color" name="color"><br><br>

    <!-- Submit button -->
    <input type="submit" value="Book Appointment">
  </form>
</body>
</html>



 Q4. Feedback Form with Range and Search: Develop a feedback form that includes:
Rating (range input with a label indicating the value)
Search for a specific product/service (search input)
User's website (URL input)
Phone number (tel input)
Submit button
Structuring Forms with Fieldset and Legend:


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Feedback Form</title>
  <script>
    // Simple script to show the range value dynamically
    function showRating(value) {
      document.getElementById("ratingValue").innerText = value;
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Feedback Form</h1>

  <!-- Feedback form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Group all fields using fieldset -->
    <fieldset>
      <legend>Provide Your Feedback</legend>

      <!-- Rating with range -->
      <label for="rating">Rate our Service (1â€“10):</label><br>
      <input type="range" id="rating" name="rating" min="1" max="10" value="5" 
             oninput="showRating(this.value)">
      <span id="ratingValue">5</span><br><br>

      <!-- Search input -->
      <label for="search">Search Product/Service:</label><br>
      <input type="search" id="search" name="search" placeholder="Enter product/service"><br><br>

      <!-- Website input -->
      <label for="website">Your Website:</label><br>
      <input type="url" id="website" name="website" placeholder="https://example.com"><br><br>

      <!-- Phone input -->
      <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label><br>
      <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="+91-9876543210"><br><br>

      <!-- Submit button -->
      <input type="submit" value="Submit Feedback">
    </fieldset>
  </form>
</body>
</html>



Q5. Multi-Section Application Form: Create an application form divided into sections using <fieldset> and <legend>:
Personal Information: Name, Address, Phone, Email
Educational Background: Degree, University, Graduation Year
Experience: Job Title, Company, Years of Experience (textarea for description)
Submit button
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Application Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Application Form</h1>

  <!-- Form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Personal Information Section -->
    <fieldset>
      <legend>Personal Information</legend>
      
      <label for="name">Full Name:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

      <label for="address">Address:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="address" name="address" required><br><br>

      <label for="phone">Phone:</label><br>
      <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="+91-9876543210"><br><br>

      <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>
    </fieldset>

    <br>

    <!-- Educational Background Section -->
    <fieldset>
      <legend>Educational Background</legend>
      
      <label for="degree">Degree:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="degree" name="degree" required><br><br>

      <label for="university">University:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="university" name="university"><br><br>

      <label for="gradyear">Graduation Year:</label><br>
      <input type="number" id="gradyear" name="gradyear" min="1900" max="2100"><br><br>
    </fieldset>

    <br>

    <!-- Experience Section -->
    <fieldset>
      <legend>Work Experience</legend>
      
      <label for="jobtitle">Job Title:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="jobtitle" name="jobtitle"><br><br>

      <label for="company">Company:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="company" name="company"><br><br>

      <label for="years">Years of Experience:</label><br>
      <input type="number" id="years" name="years" min="0" max="50"><br><br>

      <label for="desc">Job Description:</label><br>
      <textarea id="desc" name="desc" rows="4" cols="40"></textarea><br><br>
    </fieldset>

    <br>

    <!-- Submit Button -->
    <input type="submit" value="Submit Application">
  </form>
</body>
</html>


Q6. Feedback Form: 
Build a simple feedback or contact form with: 
Name (text) 
Email (email) 
Subject (text) 
Message (textarea) 
File upload for attachments (file, with type="file")

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Feedback Form</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Feedback Form</h1>

  <!-- Feedback form starts -->
  <form>
    <!-- Name -->
    <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br><br>

    <!-- Email -->
    <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br><br>

    <!-- Subject -->
    <label for="subject">Subject:</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject"><br><br>

    <!-- Message -->
    <label for="message">Message:</label><br>
    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" cols="40"></textarea><br><br>

    <!-- File Upload -->
    <label for="file">Attach File:</label><br>
    <input type="file" id="file" name="file"><br><br>

    <!-- Submit Button -->
    <input type="submit" value="Submit Feedback">
  </form>
</body>
</html>


